mainpitch.description: I'm a problem solver/fullstack software engineer/writer/seo. I've helped businesses like Sandals, Jumio, and TeamiBlends grow their websites through SEO and PR strategies. I work for a digital marketing agency called From The Future.

frontmatter.description: Learning new things and taking on new and interesting projects has been my passion. If you'd be interested in having me help improve your business, website, or social media campaign, feel free to take a look at what I have to offer by clicking the button below.
